bucket-list%20hunting%20trip%20on%20a%20Canadian%20island%2C%20visited%20his%20father%20in%20Bulgaria%2C%20took%20his%20kids%20to%20Disney%20World%2C%20and%20whisked%20my%20sister%20away%20for%20a%20romantic%20tour%20of%20Italy%20and%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20share%20his%20story%20with%20you%20to%20illustrate%20something%20that's%20easy%20to%20forget%20when%20life%20feels%20exhausting%20and%20your%20dreams%20are%20taking%20longer%20than%20you%20hoped%20to%20achieve%3A%20The%20best%20indicator%20of%20how%20far%20you'll%20go%20isn't%20where%20you've%20landed%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20how%20far%20you've%20already%20come.%20You%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-abroad-feel-like-home-diplomat-life-coach-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20a%20new%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20something%20many%20people%20never%20accomplish%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20working%20in%20a%20position%20with%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20career%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20please%2C%20do%20me%20a%20favor%3A%20Look%20at%20your%20accomplishments%20and%20congratulate%20yourself.%20You're%20a%20rockstar%20with%20remarkable%20inner%20strength%20and%20intelligence%2C%20and%20while%20I%20know%20you're%20tired%2C%20you're%20going%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20your%20own%20history%20is%20a%20much%20stronger%20data%20point%20for%20where%20you%20%26quot%3Bshould%20be%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20your%20peers.%20You%20mentioned%20seeing%20other%20people%20your%20age%20%26quot%3Bwasting%20money%20on%20drinks.%26quot%3B%20Your%20use%20of%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bwasting%26quot%3B%20tells%20me%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-sober-non-alcoholic-economy-restaurants-events-boom-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earen't%20much%20of%20a%20drinker%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Apparently%2C%20they%20are%2C%20and%20therefore%20see%20drinking%20as%20a%20worthy%20financial%20trade-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20you%20cannot%20fall%20into%20a%20comparison%20trap%20with%20your%20peers.%20You're%20different%20people%20on%20your%20own%20journeys.%20Instead%2C%20spend%20that%20energy%20analyzing%20your%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-plan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinancial%20priorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20aligning%20them%20with%20your%20spending%20habits.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20turn%20your%20abstract%20fantasies%20into%20concrete%20goals%20and%20make%20choices%20based%20on%20those%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20extremely%20specific%20about%20what%20matters%20most%20to%20you%20financially%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-budget%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20your%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20those%20priorities.%20If%20travel%20matters%20more%20to%20you%20than%20clothes%2C%20eating%20out%2C%20or%20nightlife%2C%20create%20a%20separate%20sinking%20fund%20for%20holidays%20and%20automatically%20transfer%20money%20into%20it%20every%20payday%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20only%20%E2%82%AC100%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20the%20same%20for%20other%20goals%20that%20matter%20to%20you%2C%20whether%20that's%20dating%2C%20buying%20new%20clothes%2C%20or%20taking%20time%20off%20work.%20Saving%20becomes%20much%20easier%20when%20your%20money%20has%20a%20clear%20purpose%20attached%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20look%20for%20ways%20to%20reach%20your%20goals%20in%20a%20more%20budget-friendly%20way.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froommates-30s-cheap-rent-company-pros-cons-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGet%20roommates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20rent%2C%20if%20you%20can.%20Buy%20your%20clothes%20at%20thrift%20stores.%20Stay%20at%20hostels%20when%20you%20travel%2C%20and%20track%20airfare%20and%20train%20fare%20to%20ensure%20you're