mb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAn%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelocation-europe-better-future-cant-afford-travel-feel-worthless-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780910102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a231c312e5a80cfe0504043%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelocation-europe-better-future-cant-afford-travel-feel-worthless-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%26quot%3B%20answers%20your%20relationship%20and%20money%20questions.%20This%20week%2C%20a%20reader%20struggles%20after%20moving%20to%20the%20Netherlands%20for%20a%20better%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Olivia%20Christensen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20study%20mentally%20strong%20people.%20Here%20are%205%20signs%20you're%20overwhelmed%20at%20work%20%E2%80%94%20not%20burned%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223562%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rear%20view%20wide%20shot%20of%20a%20woman%20sitting%20working%20at%20a%20computer.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a232790b4fb977f35984ff6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESolStock%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmy%20Morin%20is%20a%20psychotherapist%2C%20podcast%20host%2C%20and%20author.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20that%20many%20mislabel%20overwhelm%20as%20burnout%2C%20leading%20to%20incorrect%20solutions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOverwhelm%20is%20temporary%20and%20may%20improve%20with%20breaks%2C%20unlike%20burnout%2C%20which%20requires%20deeper%20solutions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%20two%20decades%2C%20people%20have%20walked%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftherapist-widowed-at-26-shares-how-she-worked-through-grief-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20therapy%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20told%20me%20they%20were%20burned%20out.%20Most%20of%20them%20weren't%20actually%20burned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-cutting-back-employee-wellness-benefits-fitness-money-gyms-healthcare-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECorporate%20wellness%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20social%20media%20carousels%20that%20gloss%20over%20the%20topic%20are%20leading%20to%20incorrect%20self-diagnoses.%20People%20are%20using%20%26quot%3BI'm%20burned%20out%26quot%3B%20the%20way%20they%20used%20to%20say%20%26quot%3BI'm%20tired.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20concluded%20you%20have%20burnout%2C%20you'll%20look%20for%20evidence%20to%20confirm%20it.%20Every%20time%20you%20feel%20bored%20in%20a%20meeting%20or%20overwhelmed%20by%20a%20full%20schedule%2C%20you'll%20chalk%20it%20up%20to%20more%20evidence%20that%20you're%20burned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20understand%20the%20temptation.%20Calling%20it%20burnout%20makes%20the%20feeling%20feel%20legitimate.%20But%20if%20you%20mislabel%20overwhelm%20as%20burnout%2C%20you'll%20reach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstressed-at-work-rage-rooms-ax-throwing-layoffs-ai-burnout-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efor%20solutions%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20don't%20fit%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurnout%2C%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F28-05-2019-burn-out-an-occupational-phenomenon-international-classification-of-diseases%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Health%20Organization%20defines%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20chronic%20workplace%20stress%20that%20has%20gone%20unmanaged%20for%20so%20long%20it%20produces%20three%20things%3A%20exhaustion%2C%20cynicism%2C%20and%20reduced%20effectiveness%20at%20work.%20Overwhelm%20is%20a%20temporary%20issue%20that%20can%20be%20addressed%20by%20tackling%20the%20problem%20at%20hand.%20If%20you%20insist%20you're%20burned%20out%2C%20you%20might%20think%20the%20only%20solution%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-six-figure-job-burnout-working-freelance-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equitting%20your%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20miss%20out%20on%20taking%20the%20action%20that%20would%20actually%20give%20you%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20signs%20you're%20overwhelmed%2C%20not%20burned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207eb47c9-7ee2-4a30-a211-8aa8f53f199e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20You%20still%20care.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20frustrated%20about%20the%20obstacles%20that%20stand%20in%20your%20way%20and%20prevent%20you%20from%20turning%20in%20your%20best%20work%2C%20you're%20overwhelmed.%20If%20you've%20genuinely%20stopped%20caring%20about%20the%20outcome%2C%20that's%20closer%20to%20burnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20aren't%20sure%20which%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20you're%20on%2C%20imagine%20yourself%20turning%20in%20some%20incredible%20work%20this%20week.%20Would%20that%20still%20mean%20something%20to%20you%3F%20If%20so%2C%20you're%20temporarily%20overwhelmed%2C%20not%20permanently%20burned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4ca8bf4-ba95-4610-bbf2-fdd63eb47005%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20A%20great%20weekend%20gives%20you%20relief.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20come%20back%20to%20work%20on%20a%20Monday%20feeling%20even%20the%20slightest%20bit%20restored%2C%20you're%20just%20overwhelmed.%20Two%20days%20off%20isn't%20meant%20to%20fix%20everything%2C%20but%20a%20break%20from%20the%20grind%20should%20move%20the%20needle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2C%20however%2C%20an%20amazing%20weeklong%20vacation%20leaves%20you%20feeling%20as%20frazzled%20as%20when%20you%20left%2C%20you%20might%20be%20burned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20caveat%3A%20Look%20at%20how%20you're%20spending%20your%20days%20off.%20If%20you're%20sprinting%20from%20one%20activity%20to%20the%20next%20and%20don't%20take%20time%20to%20rest%2C%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20judge%20how%20your%20time%20off%20affects%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c609b741-e13b-433a-8aea-363e6e38a736%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20want%20to%20do%20the%20work%2C%20but%20there's%20too%20much%20to%20do.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20overwhelmed%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20think%2C%20%3Cem%3EI%20have%20too%20much%20to%20do%20and%20not%20enough%20time%20to%20do%20it%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Cutting%20down%20on%20your%20to-do%20list%2C%20asking%20for%20help%2C%20or%20checking%20things%20off%20the%20list%20should%20help%20you%20feel%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20burned%20out%2C%20however%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20think%2C%20%3Cem%3EI%20can't%20make%20myself%20get%20my%20tasks%20done%20and%20I%20don't%20care%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Burnout%20involves%20a%20lack%20of%20meaning%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-quitting-made-my-work-burnout-worse-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ezaps%20your%20effort%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20prevents%20you%20from%20experiencing%20a%20sense%20of%20accomplishment%20when%20you%20get%20something%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22626cb75f-eefb-4cb9-b2db-5c42f0e6e0fd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20You%20can%20see%20the%20finish%20line.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20overwhelmed%2C%20you%20can%20still%20see%20the%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20You%20know%20once%20your%20deadline%20passes%20or%20Friday%20afternoon%20arrives%2C%20you'll%20feel%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20burned%20out%2C%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20other%20side.%20You%20won't%20imagine%20anything%20that%20brings%20relief.%20Instead%2C%20you'll%20think%20about%20how%20finishing%20one%20thing%20means%20starting%20the%20next%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20keep%20going%20feels%20unsustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de7fe770-0c40-4f70-99c0-e35797847cc9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20The%20physical%20toll%20is%20evident.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20overwhelmed%2C%20your%20shoulders%20might%20get%20tight%2C%20your%20stomach%20might%20churn%2C%20and%20you%20might%20struggle%20to%20sleep%20because%20you're%20thinking%20about%20all%20the%20things%20you%20need%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20body%20is%20yelling%20at%20you%2C%20that's%20actually%20a%20good%20sign.%20It%20means%20your%20system%20is%20still%20responding%20to%20the%20stress.%20It%20wants%20you%20to%20take%20action.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-yoga-tips-longtime-yogi-things-wish-i-knew-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20little%20yoga%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20gentle%20stretching%2C%20and%20regular%20exercise%20can%20help%20you%20feel%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20burned%20out%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20feel%20flat%20or%20numb%2C%20both%20physically%20and%20emotionally.%20My%20therapy%20clients%20who%20are%20genuinely%20burned%20out%20will%20say%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20feel%20stressed%20anymore.%20I%20feel%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22074497ae-3b0c-4a58-8f17-cc22bcdf7fda%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20do%20when%20you've%20named%20it%20correctly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20overwhelmed%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20new%20job%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbala-bangles-founder-burnout-recovery-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20six-month%20sabbatical%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20need%20a%20strategy%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem.%20Name%20exactly%20what%20you're%20feeling%20instead%20of%20calling%20it%20all%20%26quot%3Bstress.%26quot%3B%20Use%20the%2010-minute%20rule%20to%20tackle%20a%20task%20you've%20been%20avoiding%20%E2%80%94%20commit%20to%2010%20minutes%20to%20build%20some%20momentum%20that%20will%20help%20you%20keep%20going.%20Or%20gamify%20the%20grind%2C%20so%20you%20can%20get%20more%20tasks%20done%20faster.%20These%20are%20three%20examples%20of%20strategies%20I%20address%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famymorinlcsw.com%2Fbooks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20book%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20give%20you%20fast%20relief%20when%20you're%20feeling%20overwhelmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20burned%20out%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20more%20serious%20intervention%20%E2%80%94%20like%20extended%20time%20off%2C%20therapy%2C%20or%20a%20major%20shift%20in%20your%20role.%20If%20you%20aren't%20sure%20if%20you're%20burned%20out%2C%20talk%20to%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%20if%20you%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurnout%20responds%20to%20the%20right%20care%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20name%20it%20correctly%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychotherapist-shares-how-to-know-overwhelmed-vs-burned-out-work-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780910041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a232770b4fb977f35984ff5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%2