rom%20AI%20in%20just%20about%20every%20aspect%20of%20its%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20to%20see%20this%20firsthand%20during%20its%20annual%20shareholders%20meeting%20at%20its%20headquarters%20in%20Bentonville%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20where%20executives%20and%20frontline%20workers%20shared%20how%20the%20technology%20is%20transforming%20retail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c505bdc-c07c-415d-8459-495e7a156e90%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20for%20everyone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20Walmart%20is%20using%20its%20scale%20to%20its%20advantage%20by%20equipping%20people%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20the%20company%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-ai-coding-tool-limit-duplicative-requests-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etools%20to%20wrangle%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20democratize%20the%20access%20to%20learning%20and%20democratize%20the%20access%20to%20making%20a%20difference%2C%20so%20that%20people%20can%20learn%20and%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20John%20Furner%20told%20reporters%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221746%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walmart%20CEO%20John%20Furner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2487d52e5a80cfe050436f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalmart%20CEO%20John%20Furner.%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20talked-about%20example%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-code-puppy-ai-anthropic-claude-code-openai-codex-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20Code%20Puppy%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Walmart%20Global%20Tech%20distinguished%20engineer%20Mike%20Pfaffenberger%20built%20and%20shared%20with%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20already%20has%20a%20dizzying%20number%20of%20agents%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20super-agents%20tailored%20for%20particular%20use%20cases%2C%20but%20Code%20Puppy%20was%20notable%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20help%20people%20across%20the%20organization%20vibecode%20their%20own%20solutions%20%E2%80%94%20from%20salaried%20software%20engineers%20to%20hourly%20forklift%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20companies%20that%20may%20centralize%20AI%20development%20within%20traditionally%20tech-focused%20departments%2C%20Walmart's%20approach%20accelerates%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20new%20ideas%20can%20arise%20from%20the%20front%20lines%20and%20spread%20throughout%20the%20global%20enterprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20where%20the%20idea%20came%20from.%20It%20could%20be%20in%20Bangalore.%20It%20could%20be%20in%20Greater%20Toronto.%20It%20could%20be%20Mexico%20City.%20It%20could%20be%20in%20Wichita%2C%20Kansas.%20Wherever%20the%20best%20idea%20is%2C%20we%20should%20take%20that%20and%20scale%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Furner%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20simply%20surface%20what's%20already%20been%20built%2C%20and%20then%20we%20see%20the%20adoption%20rates%20go%20much%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b145f85a-9d1d-4c1e-b58e-9ac77a1ad317%5C%22%3ESome%20workers%20want%20better%20guardrails%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart's%20embrace%20of%20AI%20is%20not%20without%20controversy%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20shareholder%20proposal%20backed%20by%20United%20for%20Respect%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20retail%20workers%2C%20criticized%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20and%20automation%20on%20frontline%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAva%20Williams%2C%20an%20overnight%20stocker%20in%20Washington%2C%20presented%20the%20proposal%20during%20the%20Walmart%20shareholders%20meeting.%20She%20said%20the%20new%20AI-powered%20workflows%20push%20workers%20like%20her%20to%20cut%20corners%20as%20they%20race%20against%20unrealistic%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20asking%20Walmart%20to%20stop%20using%20technology.%20We%20are%20asking%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-online-grocery-delivery-boom-is-stretching-store-workers-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnology%20that%20works%20for%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20against%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShareholders%20rejected%20the%20measure%2C%20and%20the%20company%20said%20it%20has%20multiple%20channels%20for%20employees%20to%20share%20their%20ideas%20and%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Walmart%20associate's%20blue%20vest.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a24883ab4fb977f35985277%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20officially%20launched%20a%20credentialing%20program%20it%20built%20with%20OpenAI%20that%20is%20available%20to%20every%20employee%2C%20fulfilling%20a%20commitment%20it%20announced%20back%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20program%20is%20intended%20to%20help%20employees%20build%20practical%20confidence%20with%20AI.%20They%20learn%20to%20integrate%20the%20tools%20into%20the%20problems%20they%20face%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20highlighted%20one%20such%20case%3A%20A%20logistics%20manager%20who%20completed%20a%20Google%20AI%20certification%20and%20used%20those%20skills%20to%20develop%20an%20agent%20that%20helps%20Walmart%20identify%20routes%20that%20would%20get%20drivers%20home%20faster%20with%20fewer%20empty%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walmart%20workers%20on%20the%20headquarters%20campus%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2488c92e5a80cfe0504371%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-offering-subway-delivery-more-restaurants-may-follow-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edelivery%20partnership%20with%20in-store%20Subway%3C%2Fa%3E%20restaurants%20now%20comes%20with%20a%20hefty%20serving%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20order%20pickers%20already%20follow%20an%20AI-generated%20route%20through%20the%20store%20to%20fill%20the%20basket%2C%20and%20Walmart's%20head%20of%20digital%20fulfillment%2C%20Greg%20Cathey%2C%20said%20AI%20now%20also%20finds%20the%20right%20moment%20in%20that%20route%20to%20queue%20Subway%20workers%20to%20make%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20AI%20that's%20timing%20everything%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20sandwich%20is%20going%20to%20be%20hot%20if%20it's%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20always%20fresh%2C%26quot%3B%20Cathey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e5cc3cb-41b4-43a4-8d6b-83d4e5ba1f00%5C%22%3EDeeper%20insights%20about%20what%20customers%20really%20want%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20at%20Walmart's%20warehouse%20club%2C%20Sam's%20Club%20Director%20of%20Consumer%20Insights%20Sue%20Jervis%20said%20she%20can%20now%20gain%20new%20details%20from%20the%20chain's%20fast-growing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsams-club-membership-growing-army-in-race-against-costco-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emember%20feedback%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethanks%20to%20the%20power%20of%20multimodal%20AI%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20expressed%20a%20visceral%20disgust%20for%20five-star%20surveys%20and%20said%20the%20conversations%20and%20video%20clips%20she%20gets%20from%20participants%20give%20her%20a%20much%20more%20precise%20understanding%20of%20what%20really%20matters%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20AI%2C%20Jervis%20can%20tap%20into%20the%20150%2C000-member%20group%20and%20extract%20not%20just%20%3Cem%3Ewhat%3C%2Fem%3E%20they're%20saying%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3Ehow%3C%2Fem%3E%20they're%20saying%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20emotional%20register%20behind%20their%20feedback%20about%20the%20club's%20products%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222298%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Seth%20Dallaire%20leads%20a%20panel%20at%20Walmart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2489502ab5f9757add9e6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalmart%20Chief%20Growth%20Officer%20Seth%20Dallaire.%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20is%20also%20learning%20more%20about%20customers%20who%20use%20the%20company's%20new%20Sparky%20chatbot%2C%20which%20acts%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20personal%20shopping%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20learning%20a%20ton%20just%20from%20how%20they're%20interacting%20with%20Sparky%20relative%20to%20ways%20that%20maybe%20historically%20they%20have%20interacted%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Growth%20Officer%20Seth%20Dallaire%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20that%20interaction%20is%20significant%20enough%20that%20the%20company%20is%20not%20rushing%20to%20serve%20ads%20in%20the%20chat%2C%20focusing%20instead%20on%20ensuring%20customers%20are%20getting%20what%20they%20want%20from%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20long%20natural%20language%20query%20strings%20that%20look%20very%20different%20than%20someone%20typing%20in%20'men's%20shoes%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20really%20interesting%20piece%20of%20information%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222347%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dominick%20Reuter%20in%20the%20security%20footage%20at%20a%20Walmart%20supercenter.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a248b8db4fb977f3598527a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221173%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227924bd2d-8164-4423-9080-faa18eb8f35e%5C%22%3EBetting%