0than%20350%20interns%20who%20will%20work%20in%20areas%20including%20quantitative%20research%2C%20investment%20and%20trading%2C%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInterns%20come%20from%20more%20than%2090%20schools%20globally%2C%20with%20MIT%2C%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20Stanford%2C%20Georgia%20Tech%2C%20and%20UT%20Austin%20among%20the%20most%20represented.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAround%2090%25%20of%20the%20interns%20come%20from%20technical%20backgrounds%2C%20like%20mathematics%2C%20physics%2C%20and%20computer%20science%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20are%20finance%20and%20economics%20majors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20class%20includes%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20USA%20Computing%20Olympiad%20Platinum%20award%20winners%20and%2020%20International%20Olympiad%20medalists.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221fa56a3b-c260-4d4a-b1c4-77012ec69ecb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20select%20top%20candidates%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20select%20top%20candidates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-summer-interns-ai-banks-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInterns%20across%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20entering%20an%20industry%20transformed%20by%20AI%2C%20as%20new%20tools%20automate%20much%20of%20the%20work%20once%20synonymous%20with%20junior%20roles%20and%20firms%20incorporate%20the%20technology%20into%20training.%20Griffin%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-citadel-ai-skeptic-changes-tune-hype-jobs-finance-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonce%20a%20prominent%20AI%20skeptic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20last%20month%20that%20the%20technology%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Bprofoundly%20more%20powerful%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20can%20now%20complete%20work%20in%20hours%20that%20would%20have%20taken%20people%20with%20PhDs%20in%20finance%20weeks%2C%20even%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fabian%20Figi%20and%20Iris%20Wang%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a231a672e5a80cfe050401a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFabian%20Figi%20and%20Iris%20Wang%20lead%20campus%20recruiting%20for%20Citadel%20Securities%20and%20Citadel%2C%20respectively.%3Cp%3ECitadel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%20assessed%20applicants%20on%20their%20AI%20fluency%20during%20the%20recruitment%20process%2C%20along%20with%20their%20good%20judgment.%20Many%20of%20the%20strongest%20applicants%20knew%20how%20to%20leverage%20new%20tools%20and%20help%20AI%20code%20effectively%2C%20but%20the%20%26quot%3BA-plus%26quot%3B%20candidates%20were%20differentiated%20by%20their%20judgment%20and%20adaptability%2C%20Wang%20said.%20Figi%20said%20that%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-a-job-citadel-securities-ai-skills-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoft%20skills%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20especially%20important%2C%20a%20traditional%20STEM%20degree%20still%20holds%20weight%2C%20even%20if%20the%20traditional%20STEM%20skills%20aren't%20as%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20like%20people%20who%20pursue%20STEM%20degrees%20not%20just%20because%20of%20their%20technical%20expertise%2C%20but%20because%20it's%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20people%20who%20want%20to%20challenge%20themselves%2C%20and%20it%20requires%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20raw%20intellectual%20horsepower%20that%20will%20push%20them%20forward%20no%20matter%20how%20tools%20evolve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20interns%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20have%20more%20time%20to%20think%20about%20higher-order%2C%20complex%20problems%2C%20which%20will%20likely%20make%20the%20role%20%26quot%3Bmore%20interesting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb5b4ab9-4693-43be-a62a-a657cce916b9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Return%20offers%20and%20evaluation%5C%22%3EReturn%20offers%20and%20evaluation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20intern%20role%20itself%20is%20changing%2C%20Citadel%20and%20Citadel%20Securities%20are%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-summer-internship-advice-success-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevaluating%20interns%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20much%20the%20same%20way%3A%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterns%20work%20on%20team%20projects%20with%20real%20business%20implications%20and%20have%20access%20to%20the%20same%20suite%20of%20AI%20tools%20as%20full-time%20employees%2C%20Wang%20and%20Figi%20said.%20They%20have%20one-on-one%20conversations%20with%20their%20managers%20each%20week%20and%20ongoing%20communication%20with%20team%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summer%2C%20interns%20present%20their%20projects%20to%20business%20leaders%2C%20and%20Griffin%20and%20Citadel%20Securities%20CEO%20Peng%20Zhao%20review%20return%20offers.%20Figi%20said%20that%20while%20it's%20hard%20to%20predict%20how%20the%20summer%20will%20shake%20out%2C%20he%20expects%20most%20interns%20to%20get%20a%20return%20offer%2C%20as%20they%20have%20in%20past%20years.%20The%20companies%20don't%20have%20specific%20quotas%20for%20returns%2C%20and%20instead%20evaluate%20whether%20each%20intern%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bwildly%20successful%26quot%3B%20individually%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20track%20record%20is%20pretty%20good%3A%20campus%20hires%20are%20around%20twice%20as%20likely%20to%20one%20day%20be%20considered%20high%20performers%2C%20based%20on%20annual%20performance%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20have%20an%20almost%20insatiable%20appetite%20for%20exceptional%20talent%2C%20and%20we'll%20continue%20trying%20to%20identify%20as%20much%20of%20it%20as%20we%20can%20because%20we%20believe%20it's%20a%20critical%20competitive%20advantage%2C%26quot%3B%20Figi%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20identify%20that%20talent%2C%20we'll%20move%20incredibly%20fast%20to%20secure%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInterning%20on%20Wall%20Street%20this%20summer%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aatecotzky%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eatecotzky%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20alicetecotzky.05.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-citadel-securities-summer-intern-competitive-hedge-fund-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780909741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a23352bb4fb977f35985070%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-citadel-securities-summer-intern-competitive-hedge-fund-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Citadel%20and%20Citadel%20Securities%20accepted%20a%20record-low%200.36%25%20of%20interns%20but%20have%20the%20largest%20class%20ever%2C%20as%20hedge%20funds%20work%20to%20build%20talent%20pipelines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20to%20cheer%20on%20Knicks%20at%20NBA%20Finals%20game%20in%20New%20York%20City%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780909739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0b