s%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDemocratic%20lawmakers%20are%20pushing%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20deliver%20student-debt%20relief%20to%20eligible%20borrowers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20also%20urged%20the%20department%20to%20continue%20the%20pause%20on%20involuntary%20collections%20and%20stop%20the%20transfer%20to%20the%20Treasury.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20push%20comes%20as%20student-loan%20defaults%20are%20at%20a%20record%20high.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-moving-student-loan-debt-default-resolution-fsa-borrowers-repayment-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20in%20default.%20Lawmakers%20want%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20keep%20more%20from%20falling%20deeper%20into%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20and%20Jeff%20Merkley%2C%20and%20Reps.%20Ayanna%20Pressley%20and%20Andr%C3%A9%20Carson%2C%20led%20over%2060%20of%20their%20Democratic%20colleagues%20in%20pushing%20Education%20Sec.%20Linda%20McMahon%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-back-on-ibr-borrowers-debt-relief-processing-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprovide%20student-debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20eligible%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20want%20the%20administration%20to%20cancel%20student%20debt%20for%20borrowers%20who%20qualified%20for%20relief%20under%20existing%20programs%2C%20including%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%2C%20the%20Total%20and%20Permanent%20Disability%20discharge%2C%20and%20borrower%20defense%20to%20repayment%2C%20while%20also%20clearing%20the%20backlog%20of%20income-driven%20repayment%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefaults%20are%20at%20a%20record%20high%20%E2%80%94%207.7%20million%20borrowers%20were%20in%20default%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20with%20another%203%20million%20in%20delinquency.%20The%20lawmakers%20wrote%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loan-debt-repayment-overhaul-final-rule-new-plans-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esweeping%20student-loan%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20include%20new%20repayment%20plans%2C%20the%20elimination%20of%20SAVE%2C%20and%20the%20planned%20transfer%20of%20defaulted%20accounts%20to%20the%20Treasury%2C%20could%20push%20more%20borrowers%20into%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20administration's%20failure%20to%20meaningfully%20address%20the%20default%20crisis%20has%20raised%20Americans'%20costs%20and%20tanked%20borrowers'%20ability%20to%20access%20credit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawmakers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unacceptable%20that%20debt%20cancellation%20that%20borrowers%20are%20legally%20entitled%20to%20has%20been%20delayed%20and%20denied%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20Trump's%20student-loan%20changes%20affect%20you%3F%20Are%20you%20preparing%20for%20higher%20monthly%20payments%20or%20changing%20your%20educational%20plans%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7Td2yVsmvM31yKsT6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwage-garnishment-paused-student-loan-borrowers-in-default-linda-mcmahon-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epaused%20involuntary%20collections%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20defaulted%20borrowers%20while%20preparing%20to%20implement%20its%20coming%20repayment%20changes.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20are%20also%20urging%20the%20department%20to%20extend%20the%20pause%2C%20holding%20off%20on%20wage%20garnishment%20and%20the%20seizure%20of%20federal%20benefits.%20The%20department%20is%20also%20preparing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-transferring-treasury-education-department-dismantling-debt-repayment-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etransfer%20defaulted%20student-loan%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Treasury%2C%20and%20the%20lawmakers%20said%20that%20the%20transfer%20should%20be%20stopped%20to%20continue%20relief%20for%20defaulted%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20push%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20Trump's%20sweeping%20student-loan%20repayment%20overhaul%20will%20go%20into%20effect%20on%20July%201.%20Many%20borrowers%20are%20preparing%20for%20higher%20monthly%20payments%2C%20some%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20more%2C%20due%20to%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20which%20would%20have%20allowed%20for%20cheaper%20payments%20and%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20debt%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Kent%2C%20the%20department's%20undersecretary%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20changes%20%26quot%3Bwill%20ensure%20students%20continue%20to%20have%20the%20access%20that%20they%20need%20for%20federal%20student%20loans%2C%20while%20helping%20prevent%20borrowers%20from%20taking%20on%20unmanageable%20debt%20levels%20that%20they%20may%20never%20be%20able%20to%20repay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20asked%20that%20McMahon%20provide%20information%20on%20the%20coming%20changes%2C%20including%20when%20the%20department%20plans%20to%20resume%20involuntary%20collections%20and%20an%20update%20on%20the%20debt%20relief%20backlog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20student%20loans%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C