VYa2s5NUZPc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQQMjIyMDM5MTc4ODIwMDg5MgABHnyoHjCFv6ImxsKZAVb6KMNjtFytRwjS8JroPUPD6Y14uTg0mAms8K-UNvvZ_aem_mvBkxd5wMgrh0eiEwFe9Pw%26utm_campaign%3Dmrf-business-marfeel-headline-graphic%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26mrfcid%3D202606036a203009db341b1a07402cbe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebidding%20wars%20for%20homes.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Now%2C%20with%20SpaceX%20preparing%20to%20go%20public%20this%20week%20in%20what%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20IPO%20in%20history%2C%20the%20coastal%20neighborhoods%20around%20SpaceX's%20sprawling%20Hawthorne%20hub%20are%20hoping%20for%20their%20own%20liftoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20LA's%20Google%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Tourtellotte%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20LaTerra%20Development%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20real%20estate%20investment%20management%20and%20development%20company%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20referring%20to%20Google's%202004%20IPO%20that%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20minted%20over%20900%20millionaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long-awaited%20SpaceX%20IPO%20will%20dwarf%20Google's%2C%20finally%20turning%20paper%20wealth%20into%20cash%20for%20not%20hundreds%2C%20but%20thousands%20of%20current%20and%20former%20employees%20in%20Southern%20California.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20you%20will%20wake%20up%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20thousands%20of%20brand-new%20millionaires%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20big%20for%20LA.%20We%20needed%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20SpaceX%20shifted%20its%20headquarters%20to%20Texas%20in%202024%2C%20its%20Hawthorne%20manufacturing%20hub%20remained%20a%20major%20local%20employer%2C%20with%207%2C661%20workers%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityofhawthorne.org%2Fhome%2Fshowpublisheddocument%2F8651%2F639045891306830000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20city%20records.%3C%2Fa%3E%20With%20the%20company's%20IPO%20expected%20to%20value%20it%20at%20around%20%241.75%20trillion%2C%20and%20many%20employees%20having%20joined%20early%2C%20local%20realtors%20are%20bracing%20for%20a%20potential%20influx%20of%20newly%20wealthy%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20on%20everyone's%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Los%20Angeles%20real%20estate%20agent%20Nina%20Kubicek.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20two%20decades%20in%20the%20making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX's%20mega%20offering%20makes%20Southern%20California's%20last%20major%20tech%20IPO%20look%20quaint%20in%20comparison%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Flifestyle%2Flifestyle-news%2Fla-hood-snapchat-millionaires-will-snap-up-houses-post-ipo-957063%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnap's%202017%20debut%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20valued%20the%20Venice%20Beach-based%20social%20media%20company%20at%20about%20%2424%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20anyone%20looking%20for%20a%20boost%20for%20Los%20Angeles%20as%20a%20whole%20will%20be%20disappointed%2C%20according%20to%20Paul%20Habibi%2C%20a%20lecturer%20of%20finance%20and%20real%20estate%20at%20UCLA's%20Anderson%20School%20of%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20expect%20a%20real%20but%20diffuse%20effect%2C%20concentrated%20in%20the%20South%20Bay%20around%20Hawthorne%20rather%20than%20the%20citywide%20jolt%20a%20trillion-dollar%20listing%20might%20imply%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Habibi.%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20its%20longest-tenured%20people%20have%20already%20turned%20equity%20into%20cash%20through%20years%20of%20secondary%20sales%2C%20so%20the%20IPO%20mints%20fewer%20brand-new%20local%20millionaires%20than%20the%20headline%20suggests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3ba3dbd-1956-4b92-9a3e-0e400fe40b87%5C%22%3EAgents%20offer%20a%20special%20program%20for%20SpaceX%20employees%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20in%20the%20South%20Bay%20say%20they%20have%20already%20been%20seeing%20interest%20from%20employees%20whose%20long-held%20private%20stock%20could%20soon%20become%20life-changing%20liquidity%2C%20as%20well%20as%20from%20other%20buyers%20eager%20to%20close%20before%20the%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20went%20under%20contract%20with%20buyers%20on%20a%20house%20in%20Manhattan%20Beach%2C%20and%20they%20specifically%20articulated%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20sure%20to%20get%20something%20under%20contract%20before%20all%20the%20SpaceX%20money%20comes%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dave%20Fratello%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Edge%20Real%20Estate%20Agency%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mbconfidential.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblogs%20about%20local%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20a%20hype%20aspect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20have%20worked%20with%20SpaceX%20employees%20for%20many%20years%2C%20we've%20seen%20a%20significant%20spike%20this%20year%20in%20the%20number%20of%20former%20and%20current%20employees%20we%20are%20advising%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephanie%20Younger%2C%20whose%20real%20estate%20firm%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20niche%20helping%20SpaceX%20employees%20count%20their%20restricted%20stock%2C%20known%20as%20RSUs%2C%20toward%20their%20income%20to%20qualify%20for%20a%20bigger%20mortgage%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20employees%20will%20be%20constrained%20by%20lock-up%20periods%2C%20meaning%20the%20real%20spike%20in%20home%20prices%20will%20begin%20in%20September%2C%20according%20to%20Younger.%20Like%20any%20good%20real%20estate%20agent%2C%20Younger%20is%20advising%20clients%20to%20act%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20a%20SpaceX%20employee%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20area%20and%20you%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20the%20right%20signal%20to%20act%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstephanieyounger.com%2Fblog-spacex-ipo-filing-rsu-mortgage-west-la-2026%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYounger%20wrote%20on%20a%20blog%20post%20after%20the%20S-1%20came%20out.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BStart%20the%20search%20with%20urgency%20but%20without%20panic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8e17ea1-dba7-44ff-8b77-aeb470353016%5C%22%3EA%20boom%20for%20Manhattan%20Beach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGio%20Altamura%2C%20a%20South%20Bay%20residential%20real%20estate%20agent%2C%20said%20Manhattan%20Beach%20would%20likely%20benefit%20the%20most%20because%20it%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bepicenter%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20area's%20luxury%20housing%20market%2C%20with%20strong%20schools%2C%20prime%20oceanfront%20views%2C%20and%20a%20commute%20to%20SpaceX%20of%20just%2010%20to%2015%20minutes.%20The%20average%20home%20is%20worth%20%243%2C260%2C960%2C%20up%205%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20going%20to%20be%20affected%20positively%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20asking%20me%20who's%20going%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%2C%20it's%20always%20the%20highest%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Altamura%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20floor%20just%20gets%20raised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustin%2C%20Texas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fchrispowersjr_apparently-160-people-in-austin-tx-may-activity-7458504576649043968-1D8U%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAAAU6WFMBdtyujlmRzNI3H_rkJb_gaSpEIsQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20also%20hoping%20for%20a%20boost%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Space's%20IPO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bizjournals.com%2Faustin%2Fnews%2F2026%2F05%2F26%2Fspacex-bastrop-county-starlink-incentives.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%201%2C590%20employees%20%3C%2Fa%3Eworking%20in%20nearby%20Bastrop%20County.%20Already%2C%20Northern%20California%20has%20seen%20the%20effect%2C%20with%20one%20of%20the%20priciest%20home%20sales%20in%20the%20country%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20SpaceX%20board%20member%20and%20early%20investor%20Steve%20Jurvetson%20shattered%20La