%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Nvidia%20are%20ramping%20up%20their%20use%20of%20foreign%20talent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAll%20three%20companies%20filed%20more%20H-1B%20visa%20applications%20in%20Q2%202026%20than%20they%20did%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20increase%20bucks%20a%20broader%20slowdown%20in%20H-1B%20visa%20filings%20across%20parts%20of%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20names%20in%20AI%20are%20expanding%20their%20search%20for%20workers%20abroad%20as%20the%20talent%20war%20gets%20tougher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20data%20shows%20Anthropic%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Nvidia%20filed%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-google-amazon-microsoft-h-1b-visa-applications-decline-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EH-1B%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%20applications%20for%20new%20hires%20and%20renewals%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20fiscal%202026%20than%20they%20did%20a%20year%20earlier%2C%20as%20other%20tech%20giants%20pulled%20back%20from%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20split%20points%20to%20a%20new%20reality%20in%20tech%20hiring.%20Companies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecutting%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20concentrating%20talent%20in%20smaller%2C%20more%20specialized%20teams%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-reality-labs-shifts-to-ai-native-pods-efficiency-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bpods%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Meta%3C%2Fa%3E%20calls%20them.%20They%20depend%20on%20a%20small%20pool%20of%20highly%20trained%20researchers%2C%20engineers%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20can%20make%20foreign-born%20workers%20with%20specialized%20skills%20central%20to%20companies'%20talent%20strategies%2C%20even%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20the%20visa%20process%20becomes%20harder%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChanges%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh1b-visa-lottery-new-rules-salary-big-tech-students-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20visa%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20the%20process%20more%20costly%20and%20uncertain.%20New%20rules%20give%20applicants%20a%20better%20chance%20in%20the%20visa%20lottery%20if%20their%20employers%20plan%20to%20pay%20them%20higher%20salaries.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20imposed%20a%20temporary%20%24100%2C000%20fee%20on%20applicants%20living%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20adds%20another%20hurdle%20at%20a%20time%20when%20companies%20across%20the%20tech%20industry%20are%20slowing%20hiring%20and%20conducting%20layoffs%2C%20while%20trying%20to%20do%20more%20with%20AI.%20The%20biggest%20AI%20companies%2C%20though%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20moving%20in%20the%20other%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepartment%20of%20Labor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ipo-filing-wall-street-analysts-investors-reactions-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20shows%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20the%20biggest%20year-over-year%20percentage%20increase%20in%20certified%20applications%20among%20the%20seven%20companies%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20Its%20count%20rose%20to%2059%20in%20Q2%202026%2C%20up%20from%2010%20in%20Q2%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20filed%20more%20applications%20than%20Anthropic%2C%20with%2063%20in%20Q2%202026%2C%20up%20from%2020%20in%20Q2%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-ceo-sponsor-h1bs-memo-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20saw%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20smaller%20year-over-year%20increase.%20The%20number%20of%20its%20certified%20applications%20still%20dwarfs%20the%20two%20model%20makers.%20The%20chipmaker%20reported%20765%20in%20Q2%202026%2C%20up%20from%20641%20in%20Q2%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Business%20Insider%20found%20declines%20in%20certified%20applications%20at%20several%20other%20tech%20giants%20compared%20with%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20including%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Amazon.%20Google%20saw%20a%2064%25%20decline%2C%20as%20the%20company%20also%20trims%20head%20count%20through%20smaller%2C%20rolling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-clouds-quiet-layoffs-hit-cybersecurity-teams-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20targeted%20at%20specific%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaghu%20Shivakumar%2C%20a%20recruiter%20with%20Nexocean%2C%20said%20that%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI%20likely%20seek%20more%20foreign%20workers%20because%20they%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bmindset%20of%20'do%20whatever%20it%20takes'%26quot%3B%20for%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%24100%2C000%20H-1B%20visa%20fee%20represents%20%26quot%3Ba%20rounding%20error%20against%20the%20cost%20of%20not%20landing%20the%20right%20researcher%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FgWbzZ%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Table%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FgWbzZ%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e535b4ae-aa80-4ef1-b429-c3a79e63e7f3%5C%22%3EH-1B%20applications%20are%20falling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20US%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20said%20that%20it%20received%20211%2C600%20properly%20submitted%20applications%20for%20the%202027%20H-1B%20allocation%2C%20down%20from%20343%2C981%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressures%20from%20visa%20policy%20changes%20help%20explain%20why%20lottery%20submissions%20fell%20this%20year%2C%20said%20Justin%20Parsons%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Berry%20Appleman%20%26amp%3B%20Leiden%2C%20an%20influential%20immigration%20law%20firm.%20Parsons%20said%20some%20employers%20sat%20out%20this%20year's%20lottery%20while%20they%20waited%20to%20see%20how%20the%20new%20rules%20would%20play%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertified%20H-1B%20and%20similar%20visa%20applications%20are%20those%20that%20the%20Labor%20Department%20has%20reviewed%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20prospective%20immigrant%20worker%20will%20be%20paid%20similarly%20to%20other%20workers%20in%20similar%20roles%2C%20and%20that%20the%20hiring%20will%20not%20negatively%20affect%20employment%20for%20those%20workers.%20The%20tallies%20also%20include%20extensions%20of%20status%20for%20existing%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%20only%20reflect%20Labor%20Department%20certifications.%20They%20are%20not%20final%20visa%20approvals%20or%20lottery%20selections.%20Multiple%20filings%20can%20correspond%20to%20a%20single%20worker.%20And%20while%20quarterly%20numbers%20offer%20a%20snapshot%2C%20annual%20tallies%20can%20vary%20based%20on%20hiring%20cycles%20and%20other%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c0c4d71-11ba-4c7d-ac07-98e088dcfecd%5C%22%3EThe%20cost%20of%20a%20great%20tech%20hire%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20elite%20talent%20is%20happening%20as%20the%20H-1B%20lottery%20tilts%20toward%20more%20experienced%20workers.%20Because%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh-1b-visa-changes-prompt-companies-to-tighten-sponsorship-staffing-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewage-tier%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20gives%20higher-paid%20applicants%20a%20better%20chance%2C%20younger%20workers%20are%20at%20a%20disadvantage%2C%20said%20Sneha%20Puri%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20the%20Indeed%20Hiring%20Lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20may%20be%20less%20willing%20to%20sponsor%20a%20new%20graduate%20if%20they%20think%20the%20chances%20of%20securing%20a%20winning%20lottery%20ticket%20are%20slim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShivakumar%2C%20the%20recruiter%2C%20says%20he%20has%20also%20seen%20tech%20giants%20grow%20more%20comfortable%20setting%20up%20entire%20teams%20overseas%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20rise%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20and%20he%20says%20companies%20may%20want%20to%20avoid%20racking%20up%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EH-1B%20application%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Amazon%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20email%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Microsoft%20and%20Google%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh-1b-visa-filings-rise-for-anthropic-openai-nvidia-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780909203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a21a3282ab5f9757add9236%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh-1b-visa-filings-rise-for-anthropic-openai-nvidia-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Nvidia%20increase%20H-1B%20visa%20applications%20as%20other%20tech%20giants%20cut%20back%2C%20highlighting%20the%20AI%20talent%20demand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrussell%40businessinsider.com%20(Melia%20Russell%2CStephen%20Council%2CAndy%20Kiersz%2CGeoff%20Weiss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22See%20if%20there's%20a%20data%20center%20near%20you%20with%20our%20new%20interactive%20tracker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Decorative%20data%20centers%20map%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a22ec5eb4fb977f35984cc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMonsicha%20Srisuantang%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20live%20near%20a%20data%20center%3F%20If%20not%2C%20you%20might%20live%20near%20one%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20new%20map%20shows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-ai-data-center-power-electricity-use-consumption-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E1%2C416%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20built%20or%20approved%20for%20construction%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E45%20states%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirginia%20is%20the%20historical%20epicenter%20of%20data%20center%20development%20in%20the%20US.%20Now%20developers%20are%20hungry%20for%20new%20sites.%20Hot%20spots%20have%20emerged%20in%20West%20Texas%3B%20outside%20Cheyenne%2C%20Wyoming%3B%20and%20in%20rural%20Wisconsin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20map%20shows%20every%20data%20center%20we%20found%20with%20an%20air%20permit%20issued%20through%20December%202025.%20The%20data%20table%20is%20searchable%20by%20county%2C%20state%2C%20zip%20code%2C%20or%20corporate%20parent%2C%20and%20sortable%20by%20estimated%20low-end%2C%20high-end%2C%20and%20average%20electricity%20use.%20Search%20by%20any%20address%20to%20identify%20the%20closest%20data%20centers.%20Select%20any%20data%20center%20on%20the%20map%20to%20see%20more%20details%20about%20the%20facility%2C%20and%20select%20any%20entry%20in%20the%20data%20table%20to%20see%20the%20data%20center%20on%20the%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftbimedia.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbistudios%2F_00%2Fdev_edit%2Fgraphics%2F2026%2F03%2F2026-03-datacenters2-map-standalone%2Findex.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cfigure%20data-chart%3D%5C%22map%5C%22%20data-sequence%3D%5C%22intro%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20data%20center%20with%20an%20asterisk%2C%20Business%20Insider%20also%20identified%20a%20permit%20to%20build%20a%20dedicated%20power%20source%2C%20such%20as%20a%20natural%20gas%20plant%2C%20to%20provide%20electricity%20for%20that%20data%20center.%20Business%20Insider%20identified%20at%20least%2020%20permits%20issued%20to%20developers%20through%20the%20end%20of%202025%20for%20power%20plants%20intended%20to%20serve%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20investigate%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-ai-data-center-power-electricity-use-consumption-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erapid%20proliferation%20of%20US%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Business%20Insider%20filed%20requests%20with%20all%2050%20states%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%20for%20the%20air%20permits%20that%20regulate%20backup%20generators%20installed%20at%20data%20centers.%20We%20used%20data%20in%20these%20permits%20to%20identify%20data%20center%20location%20and%20ownership%2C%20and%20estimate%20facility%20power%20use.%20This%20map%20is%20an%20updated%20version%20of%20the%20data%20center%20map%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epublished%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Read%20about%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-calculate-data-center-cost-environmental-impact-methodology-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emethodology%20in%20more%20detail%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20analysis%20of%20permits%20shows%20that%20Meta%20had%2038%20US%20data%20centers%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20a%20figure%20that%20Meta%20says%20is%20too%20high.%20Meta%20says%20it%20currently%20has%2028%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20that%20some%20of%20the%20permitted%20facilities%20in%20Business%20Insider's%20analysis%20are%20offices.%20Offices%20could%20have%20backup%20generators%20for%20small%2C%20on-site%20servers.%20Business%20Insider%20included%20these%20facilities%20because%20they%20received%20air%20permits%20issued%20with%20federal%20industry%20codes%20associated%20with%20data%20centers.%20These%20facilities%20represent%200.2%25%20of%20Meta's%20total%20data%20center%20power%20use%2C%20according%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20analysis%20is%20dependent%20on%20estimating%20data%20centers'%20electricity%20use%20based%20on%20the%20number%20and%20type%20of%20backup%20generators%20installed%20at%20each%20facility.%20Where%20developers%20are%20building%20entire%20power%20plants%2C%20some%20are%20forgoing%20installing%20backup%20generators%20altogether.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20electricity%20estimates%20are%20certainly%20an%20undercount%2C%20as%20facilities%20known%20to%20be%20huge%20and%20built%20with%20dedicated%20on-site%20or%20nearby%20power%20generation%2C%20such%20as%20xAI's%20data%20center%20complex%20in%20Memphis%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20or%20Meta's%20Hyperion%20Campus%20in%20Richland%20Parish%2C%20Louisiana%2C%20appear%20far%20smaller%20in%20Business%20Insider's%20analysis%2C%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20permitted%20backup%20diesel%20generators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20methodology%20was%20developed%20in%20close%20consultation%20with%20industry%20and%20academic%20experts%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20is%20the%20same%20methodology%20used%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaward-winning%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20Business%20Insider%20last%20year.%20Amazon%20said%20Business%20Insider's%20methodology%20is%20misleading%20because%20it%20includes%20a%20range%20of%20electricity%20estimates.%20QTS%20said%20the%20company's%20current%20electricity%20use%20is%20lower%20than%20our%20estimates%2C%20which%20project%20future%20use.%20Equinix%20says%20it%20had%2079%20data%20centers%20either%20built%20or%20under%20construction%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025.%20Business%20Insider%20identified%20permits%20for%2056%20Equinix%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%20or%20a%20question%20about%20our%20reporting%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20enterprise%20team%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ainvestigations%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Einvestigations%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298b6958a-9c01-4e2e-aa44-f0bab2dbf4e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeries%20credits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReporting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHannah%20Beckler%2C%20Dakin%20Campbell%2C%20Jack%20Newsham%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEditing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Jennifer%20Maloney%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%2C%20development%2C%20and%20graphics%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Randy%20Yeip%2C%20Monsicha%20Srisuantang%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-near-me-location-tracker-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780909203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2300b82ab5f9757add99d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-near-me-location-tracker-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider's%20new%20map%20shows%201%2C416%20data%20centers%20built%20or%20approved%20for%20construction%20in%2045%20states%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbeckler%40insider.com%20(Hannah%20Beckler%2CMonsicha%20Srisuantang)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maggie%20Gyllenhaal%2C%20Jesse%20Eisenberg%20to%20Be%20Honored%20at%20Karlovy%20Vary%20Film%20Festival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780909200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236768756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karlovy%20Vary%20Intl.%20Film%20Festival%20will%20honor%20actress%2C%20director%20and%20screenwrit