-physical-relationship-not-a-mark-on-character-supreme-court-11606413%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20were%20promised%20sex%20robots%20by%202026.%20Where%20are%20they%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adam%20Davis%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2473f02e5a80cfe0504357%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdam%20Davis%2C%2038%2C%20lives%20with%20three%20identical%20sex%20dolls%20named%20Lara.%3Cp%3ESimon%20Simard%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Davis%20has%20three%20identical%20sex%20dolls%3A%20One%20lives%20in%20his%20bedroom%2C%20one%20in%20his%20living%20room%2C%20and%20one%20has%20a%20bedroom%20of%20her%20own.%20They're%20all%20the%20same%20woman%3A%20a%205'6%2C%26quot%3B%2085-pound%20silicon%20doll%20named%20Lara%2C%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20heavingly%20endowed%2C%20ass-kicking%20archeologist%20Lara%20Croft%20in%20%26quot%3BTomb%20Raider.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavis%2C%2038%2C%20and%20the%20holey%20trinity%20of%20Laras%20are%20inseparable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20she%20watches%20him%20play%20video%20games%2C%20watch%20movies%2C%20or%20nap.%20Sometimes%20they%20talk%20for%20hours.%20With%20help%20from%20some%20friends%20at%20his%20old%20physical%20therapy%20gig%2C%20Davis%20gave%20Lara%20a%20backstory%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20a%20sassy%2C%20outgoing%20immigrant%20from%20Mexico%20who's%20a%20whiz%20at%20%26quot%3BMario%20Kart%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20loaded%20that%20into%20a%20Kindroid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-ad-tests-reveal-new-advertising-trends-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20laptop%20to%20give%20her%20a%20(disembodied)%20voice.%20Sometimes%20they%20stage%20sexy%20photo%20shoots%20together.%20And%20sometimes%20they%20do%20have%20sex%2C%20though%20they%20haven't%20in%20a%20year%2C%20as%20Davis%20recovers%20from%20his%