s%20aren't%20yet%20mobile.%20Those%20options%20are%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20big%20Roomba%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a24772e2ab5f9757add9e50%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A4480%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A6720%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a24772e2ab5f9757add9e50%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adam%20Davis%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnDavis%20runs%20an%20Instagram%20account%20for%20Lara%2C%20where%20he%20photographs%20her%20doing%20taxes%20or%20plunging%20the%20toilet.%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnSimon%20Simard%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20ago%2C%20a%20viral%20Daily%20Sun%20article%20predicted%20that%20%26quot%3Bwomen%20will%20be%20having%20more%20sex%20with%20ROBOTS%20than%20men%20by%202025.%26quot%3B%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyougov.com%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F19285-1-4-men-would-consider-having-sex-robot%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouGov%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20the%20story%20found%201%20in%204%20American%20men%20would%20consider%20having%20sex%20with%20a%20robot.%20Mainstream%20outlets%20from%20Vox%20to%20The%20Guardian%20to%20NBC%20tr