%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-siri-bet-ai-models-commodities-google-gemini-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eversions%20of%20Siri%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20he%20returned%20in%202024%2C%20well%20into%20the%20LLM%20boom%2C%20he%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BThings%20have%20to%20have%20come%20a%20long%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20hadn't.%20The%20robots'%20skin%20and%20speech%20were%20still%20unrealistic%2C%20and%20they%20couldn't%20move%20around%20the%20conference%20floor.%20What%20was%20new%2C%20though%2C%20were%20several%20Chinese%20companies%20had%20arrived.%20(Their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-tech-founders-skipping-college-new-dropping-out-palantir-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efounders%20were%20invariably%20young%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20one%20was%20so%20young%20his%20mom%20was%20there%2C%20hovering%20in%20the%20background%2C%20McArthur%20says.)%20As%20with%20AI%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20and%20several%20other%20tech%20sectors%2C%20China's%20entrance%20into%20the%20sex%20robots%20market%20had%20knocked%20down%20the%20price%20point.%20Whereas%20American-made%20sex%20robots%20from%20the%202010s%20hype%20cycle%20typically%20started%20at%20around%20%247%2C000%20and%20quickly%20exceeded%20%2410%2C000%2C%20some%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20sell%20sex%20robots%20at%20around%20%243%2C000.%20%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20had%20gotten%20cheaper%2C%20but%20not%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20McArthur%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20Chinese%20sex%20doll%20producers%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20emails%2C%20including%20VMDoll%20and%20IronTech.%20Others%20seemed%20to%20have%20AI%20bots%20operating%20their%20WhatsApp%20messages.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20reached%20Stella%20Lau%2C%20a%20sales%20director%20for%20Jiggly%20Joy%2C%20a%20doll%20manufacturer%20based%20in%20Guangdong%20province%20with%20160%20employees.%20Lau%2C%2032%2C%20has%20worked%20for%20Jiggly%20Joy%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20long%20before%20the%20company%20released%20its%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-sex-robots-are-selling-well-realdoll-regulated-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20robot%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sex%20doll.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a24795fb4fb977f35985263%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20Lara's%20greatest%20perks%3A%20she's%20sent%20Davis'%20sleep%20quality%20%26quot%3Bway%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3Cp%3ESimon%20Simard%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJiggly%20Joy's%20new%20model%20has%20all%20the%20classic%20features%20of%20a%20sex%20robot%20%E2%80%94%20Lau%20is%20one%20of%20many%20merchants%20who%20hyped%20up%20the%20%26quot%3Bsucking%20vagina%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20suction-and-release%20pump%20system%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20it%20could%20smile%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20wave.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20blonde%20bombshell%20haircut%20and%20can%20turn%20its%20neck%20like%20M3GAN.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-startup-alfred-building-software-for-robots-and-cars-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobot%20still%20cannot%20walk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that's%20mostly%20for%20safety%20reasons%2C%20Lau%20says%3B%20she's%20too%20heavy.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20selling%20about%2021%20AI%20dolls%20a%20month%20at%20%243%2C000%2C%20Lau%20says.%20Most%20of%20the%20buyers%20are%20American%3B%20they're%20either%20former%20sex%20doll%20users%20or%20lonely%20and%20wanted%20someone%20to%20talk%20to%2C%20Lau%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20reached%20a%20representative%20for%20Formosa%20Doll%2C%20a%205-person%20Hong%20Kong-based%20distributor%20that%20works%20exclusively%20with%20Chinese%20sex%20doll%20companies.%20(He%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20his%20privacy.)%20He%20says%20AI%20sex%20robots%20are%20%26quot%3Bunderdeveloped%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20ready%20for%20sale.%20For%20one%2C%20some%20doll%20head%20prototypes%20removed%20the%20oral%20sucking%20motors%20from%20the%20mouth%20to%20make%20space%20for%20the%20AI%20voice.%20Trading%20sucking%20for%20talking%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20downside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoice%20AI%20can%20also%20be%20unpredictable%20and%20unruly%2C%20and%20sex%20doll%20users%20may%20be%20used%20to%20making%20up%20role-play%20scenarios%20in%20their%20heads%20%E2%80%94%20scenarios%20they%20have%20full%20control%20over.%20That%20makes%20him%20skeptical%20that%20AI%20robots%20would%20sell%20well.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20an%20experience%2C%20they%20want%20to%20satisfy%20a%20fantasy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20don't%20want%20something%20at%20home%20that%20talks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2479c72ab5f9757add9e52%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A5464%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A8192%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2479c72ab5f9757add9e52%3Fwidth%3D700%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sex%20dolls%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5