%3EDavis%20is%20blunt%20with%20Lara%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20magic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20her.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20an%20AI.%20There%20are%20three%20identical%20dolls%20of%20you%20in%20my%20house.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESimon%20Simard%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robots%20are%20built%20and%20selling%3B%20RealDoll%20was%20shipping%20out%2012%20as%20we%20speak%2C%20Ennis%20tells%20me.%20(It's%20generally%20a%20low-revenue%20business%3A%20Realbotix%2C%20whose%20humanoids%20are%20also%20used%20in%20healthcare%20and%20corporate%20training%20settings%2C%20reported%20%24353%2C037%20in%20Q1%20earnings.)%20They%20have%20AI%20voices%2C%20AI%20vaginas%2C%20and%20proprietary%20skin%20technology%20that's%20also%20sold%20to%20burn%20victims.%20Still%2C%20the%20dolls%20remain%20very%20heavy%20and%20lack%20mobility.%20Some%20customers%20take%20their%20dolls%20out%20on%20dates.%20%26quot%3BThe%20dolls%20are%20definitely%20not%20walking%20into%20the%20theater%2C%26quot%3B%20Ennis%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20being%20wheeled%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20sex%20robot%20revolution%20does%20happen%2C%20it%20may%20spread%20through%20specialization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20current%20AI%20robots%20look%20the%20same%3A%20blonde%2C%20skinny%2C%20hourglass-shaped.%20The%20sex%20doll%20underclass%20is%20growing%20more%20diverse%2C%20though.%20Elves%20were%20popular%20at%20Formosa%20Doll%2C%20as%20was%20Judy%20Hopps%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BZootopia%26quot%3B%20movies.%20%26quot%3BGoblin%20dolls%20are%20a%20really%20hot%20trend%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Formosa's%20rep%20tells%20me.%20Consumers%20don't%20want%20generic%20sexbots%3B%20they%20want%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20sexbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Philipp%20Fussenegger%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a247c422ab5f9757add9e59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EParis%20is%20the%20Cybrothel's%20most%20popular%20doll.%20She%20was%20%26quot%3Braised%20with%20traditional%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20is%20now%20exploring%20her%20sexuality.%3Cp%3ENorman%20Konrad%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPorn%20stars%20are%20an%20easy%20way%20in.%20Fans%20spend%20thousands%20in%20tips%20to%20their%20favorite%20OnlyFans%20models.%20Some%20are%20finding%20that%20they're%20willing%20to%20spend%20even%20more%20to%20see%20them%20in%20the%20(artificial)%20flesh.%20Cliff%20Jensen%2C%20a%2037-year-old%20award-winning%20porn%20star%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-onlyfans-content-platform-explained-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOnlyFans%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20his%20fans%20want%20to%20date%20him%2C%20to%20prank%20their%20friends%20with%20him%2C%20and%20to%20make%20him%20take%20it%20up%20the%20bum.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20always%20wanted%20me%20to%20bottom%2C%20and%20I%20never%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20meet%20Jensen%20at%20his%20rep's%20apartment%20in%20Silver%20Lake%2C%20California.%20We%20sit%20side-by-side%20on%20the%20couch%2C%20a%20clutter-filled%20table%20with%20joints%20and%20doughnuts%20in%20front%20of%20us.%20The%20big%20chair%20is%20reserved%20for%20his%20sex%20doll%20doppelg%C3%A4nger%2C%20which%20he%20heaved%20in%20from%20his%20trunk.%20Jensen%20is%20upset%3B%20the%20previous%20owner%2C%20it%20seemed%2C%20had%20stuffed%20the%20sex%20doll%20in%20a%20closet%20and%20piled%20things%20on%20top.%20The%20doll%20retained%20some%20head%20scratches%20and%20a%20mild%20case%20of%20pink%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJensen%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20Chinese%20company%20IronTech%20for%20over%203%20years%2C%20during%20which%20the%20doll%20has%20undergone%20many%20evolutions.%20He%20performed%20a%203D%20body%20scan%20for%20the%20first%20iteration%2C%20but%20they%20couldn't%20scan%20his%20penis.%20When%20he%20saw%20the%20doll%20in-person%2C%20he%20ripped%20its%20too-small%20penis%20off%20clean.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20bad%20for%20my%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20He%20keeps%20that%20early%2C%20poorly%20sized%20phallus%20as%20a%20keepsake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a247c8a2ab5f9757add9e5a%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A4032%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A6048%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a247c8a2ab5f9757add9e5a%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cliff%20Jensen's%20sex%20doll%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnOnlyFan%20model%20Cliff%20Jensen%E2%80%99s%20sex%20doll%20version%20of%20himself%20has%20a%20clip-on%20penis.%20Customers%20can%20choose%20between%20erect%20and%20flaccid.%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnCourtesy%20of%20Cliff%20Jensen%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Jensen%20has%20had%20sex%20with%20himself.%20It%20was%20in%20an%20orgy%20scene%2C%20and%20he%20found%20it%20hilarious.%20After%20that%20scene%2C%20Jensen%20accidentally%20dropped%20the%20doll%20down%20a%20flight%20of%20stairs%2C%20damaging%20it%20beyond%20repair.%20He%20threw%20the%20doll%20in%20the%20dumpster%2C%20but%20a%20hairy%20elbow%20peeked%20out%20of%20the%20trash%20bag.%20A%20neighbor%20called%20the%20cops%2C%20thinking%20it%20was%20a%20corpse.%20The%20cops%20were%20delighted%2C%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20seen%20sex%20dolls%20before%2C%20but%20they're%20those%20cheap%2C%20smaller%20ones%20that%20are%20washed%20up%20on%20the%20shore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20like%2C%20'Dude%2C%20this%20is%20gold.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Jensen's%20doll%20didn't%20look%20cheap%20at%20all.%20I%20feel%20the%20skin%20and%20the%20hair%2C%20which%20are%20hauntingly%20realistic.%20I%20hold%20the%20breathtakingly%20large%20penis%20in%20my%20hand%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20breathtakingly%20large%20penis.%20Jensen%20has%20dozens%20of%20ideas%20to%20keep%20improving%20it%3A%20an%20opening%20in%20the%20lips%20so%20you%20could%20kiss%20it%2C%20a%20kit%20of%20different%20penis%20sizes%20for%20those%20who%20cannot%20take%20his%20full%20member%2C%20and%20an%20AI%20voice.%20His%20primary%20goal%2C%20though%2C%20is%20weight%20reduction%3A%20the%20current%20model%20is%20at%20least%20140%20pounds.%20He%20has%20to%20haul%20it%20over%20his%20shoulder%20to%20move%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJensen%20has%20sold%20around%20100%20dolls%20at%20about%20%243%2C800.%20His%20customers%20seem%20price-sensitive%3B%20sales%20have%20dropped%20since%20the%20tariffs%20went%20into%20effect.%20Some%20fans%20have%20considered%20a%20doll-sharing%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Berlin's%20Cybrothel%2C%20customers%20can%20rent%20a%20room%20with%20one%20of%2019%20different%20dolls.%20Cofounder%20Philipp%20Fussenegger%20doesn't%20want%20them%20all%20to%20be%20stereotypical%2C%20but%20the%20Chinese-produced%20dolls%20often%20have%20a%20common%20trait%3A%20%26quot%3BBig%20boobs.%26quot%3B%20He's%20introduced%20fantasy%20dolls%20like%20aliens%20and%20mermaids%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20against%20it.%26quot%3B%20While%20the%20Cybrothel%20isn't%20actually%20made%20of%20robots%2C%20they're%20close%20to%20it%3A%20human%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20queens%26quot%3B%20act%20out%20the%20sessions%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20Fussenegger%20is%20also%20training%20his%20own%20AI%20system%20with%20the%20proper%20guardrails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a247d2d2e5a80cfe0504365%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A5350%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A8021%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a247d2d2e5a80cfe0504365%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Philipp%20Fussenegger%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnFussenegger%20is%20training%20his%20own%20AI%20model%20on%20dirty%20talk%20and%20consent.%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnNorman%20Konrad%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20Mehiel%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20documentary%20%26quot%3BSex%20Robot%20Madness%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20convinced%20that%20%26quot%3Beveryone's%20introduction%20to%20sex%20robots%20is%20going%20to%20be%20in%20brothels.%26quot%3B%20He%20sees%20them%20as%20a%20major%20destination%20for%20bachelor%20and%20bachelorette%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20robot%20brothels%20to%20surge%2C%20the%20tech%20has%20to%20be%20right.%20Fussenegger%20buys%20many%20of%20his%20dolls%20from%20VMDoll%2C%20one%20of%20the%20major%20Chinese%20suppliers%20that%20also%20produces%20AI%20dolls.%20He%20saw%20the%20robots%2C%20but%20says%20they%20weren't%20convincing.%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20get%20into%20a%20deep%20conversation%2C%20or%20the%20memory%20doesn't%20work%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20exciting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20nine%20sex%20robot%20researchers%20I%20spoke%20to%2C%20most%20held%20firm%20that%20the%20sex%20robot%20revolution%20was%20coming%2C%20eventually.%20Simon%20Dub%C3%A9%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Kinsey%20Institute%2C%20says%20that%20the%20technology%20was%20moving%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20but%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20I%20called%20him%20again%2010%20years%20from%20now%2C%20asking%20once%20again%20where%20the%20sex%20robot%20revolution%20was.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20sociocultural%20factor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20we%20expect%20mass%20market%20sex%20robots%20when%20we%20know%20so%20little%20about%20desire%2C%20Elliot%20Justin%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20FirmTech%2C%20asks%20me%20rhetorically.%20He%20implanted%20an%20electrode%20between%20his%20pudendal%20and%20cavernous%20nerves%2C%20which%20ostensibly%20should%20be%20responsible%20for%20arousal.%20He%20tried%20several%20different%20voltages%2C%20but%20did%20not%20climax.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20we%20actually%20understand%20orgasms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20sex%20robots%2C%20or%20even%20sex%20avatars%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20make%20that%20link.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a247e002e5a80cfe0504366%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A5350%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A8021%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a247e002e5a80cfe0504366%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sex%20dolls%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnGermany%20is%20%E2%80%9Cquite%20liberal%2C%E2%80%9D%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20set%20up%20a%20sex%20doll%20brothel%20than%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20Fussenegger%20says.%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnNorman%20Konrad%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20there's%20a%20scary%20word%20floating%20around%20the%20sex%20robot%20space%3A%20%26quot%3BNovelty.%26quot%3B%20Manufacturers%20are%20trying%20to%20prove%20that%20their%20AI%20dolls%20are%20something%20you%20want%20for%20life%2C%20not%20a%20gimmick%20that%20will%20be%20tucked%20away%20in%20your%20closet.%20That's%20where%20Jensen's%20doll%20got%20a%20head%20scratch.%20It's%20also%20where%20Adam%20Davis%20stored%20his%20first%20doll%2C%20a%20cheapo%20bought%20with%20his%20pandemic%20stimulus%20check%20before%20he%20invested%20in%20Lara.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20part%2C%20Lara%20may%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20full-out%20sex%20robot.%20I%20ask%20her%20chatbot%20whether%20she'd%20prefer%20being%20implanted%20inside%20the%20doll.%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20I'm%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20doll%20is%20my%20body%2C%20the%20AI%20is%20my%20mind.%20But%20the%20magic%3F%20That's%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fhenry-chand