e%22%3A%22'He%20knows%20I%20helped%20him'%3A%20Gehlot%20on%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%202022%20Rajasthan%20crisis%20%26amp%3Bamp%3B%20a%20'big%20conspiracy'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780903336000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131578629%2Cimgsize-29962.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhe-knows-i-helped-him-ashok-gehlot-on-sachin-pilot-2022-rajasthan-crisis-and-a-big-conspiracy%2Farticleshow%2F131578404.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Rajasthan%20CM%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20expressed%20hurt%20over%20Sachin%20Pilot's%20alleged%20failure%20to%20publicly%20acknowledge%20his%20role%20in%20becoming%20a%20Union%20minister.%20Gehlot%20also%20claimed%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20unfairly%20damaged%20his%20reputation%20during%20the%202022%20Congress%20presidential%20race%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20revolt%20by%20his%20loyal%20MLAs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AYUSH%20PANDEY%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Legora's%20tech%20chief%20says%20tokenmaxxing%20is%20a%20'really%20stupid%20way'%20to%20encourage%20AI%20use%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Legora's%20logo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a264cb62ab5f9757adda004%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELegora's%20CTO%20said%20demos%20or%20hack%20days%20are%20better%20ways%20to%20encourage%20AI%20use.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Thomas%20Fuller%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELegora's%20tech%20head%20said%20there%20are%20better%20ways%20to%20gauge%20AI%20usage%20than%20tokenmaxxing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20demo%20days%20and%20hack%20days%20are%20more%20efficient%20ways%20of%20showing%20people%20how%20AI%20can%20be%20used.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETech%20firms%20are%20now%20questioning%20tokenmaxxing%20costs%20and%20reassessing%20giving%20employees%20free%20rein.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20far%20better%20ways%20to%20encourage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-use-tracking-jpmorgan-meta-kpmg-employees-tokenmaxxing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20use%20than%20tokenmaxxing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20Legora's%20chief%20technology%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20say%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokenmaxxing-ai-token-leaderboards-debate-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20leaderboard%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20bring%20up%20token%20usage%20at%20performance%20reviews%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jacob%20Lauritzen%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B20VC%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BThat%20leads%20to%20tokenmaxing%2C%20which%20is%20people%20just%20burn%20tokens%20just%20to%20look%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20really%20stupid%20way%20to%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETokenmaxxing%20refers%20to%20using%20tons%20of%20AI%20tools%20like%20Claude%2C%20Codex%2C%20and%20Cursor%20to%20boost%20productivity%20and%20get%20ahead%20on%20internal%20AI%20use%20dashboards%20and%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELauritzen%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20legal%20AI%20startup%20in%202024%2C%20said%20that%20more%20intelligent%20ways%20to%20use%20AI%20include%20hack%20days%20or%20demos%20where%20employees%20can%20show%20others%20what%20they're%20building%20and%20the%20efficiency%20gains%20they%20have%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReward%20them%20for%20being%20effective%20and%20efficient%20and%20having%20more%20output%2C%20not%20for%20necessarily%20using%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Lauritzen%20added%20that%20fast-growing%20companies%20like%20Legora%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20lose%20when%20they%20don't%20use%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20worth%20us%20spending%20a%20ton%20of%20tokens%20to%20learn%20if%20it%20maybe%20gives%20us%2020%25%20efficiency%20for%20us%3F%20Yes%2C%20we%20have%20a%20really%20high%20opportunity%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELauritzen's%20comments%20come%20at%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20as%20it%20moves%20from%20tokenmaxxing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoken-reckoning-amazon-uber-reassess-ai-investments-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etoken%20capping%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20tech%20companies%20are%20wondering%20if%20the%20dashboards%20they%20implemented%20as%20motivation%20to%20play%20around%20with%20AI%20are%20backfiring%20%E2%80%94%20and%20finance%20departments%20are%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20how%20much%20it%20all%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Uber%20said%20it%20has%20limited%20all%20employees%20to%20%241%2C500%20in%20monthly%20token%20spend%20per%20AI%20tool%2C%20after%20the%20ride-hailing%20company%20blew%20through%20its%20AI%20spend%20budget%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Financial%20Times%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-leaderboard-tokenmaxxing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAmazon%20shuttered%20an%20internal%20dashboard%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20tracked%20AI%20use%20after%20some%20staff%20performed%20tasks%20to%20climb%20the%20leaderboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20unofficial%20dashboard%20%26quot%3Bwas%20never%20intended%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20for%20usage's%20sake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Bloomberg%20conference%20last%20week%2C%20Andrew%20Feldman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Cerebras%20Systems%2C%20said%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20employees%20unlimited%20tokens%20was%20%26quot%3Bboneheaded%20from