l%20look%20back%20at%20some%20point%20in%20time%20and%20say%20that%20was%20a%20foolish%20way%20to%20think%20about%20Nvidia%2C%26quot%3B%20Loeb%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Nvidia%20remains%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20undervalued%20when%20judged%20against%20its%20earnings%20potential%20over%20the%20next%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoeb%20suggested%20investors%20may%20be%20underestimating%20Nvidia%20because%20they%20struggle%20to%20process%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20company's%20market%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suggested%20Nvidia's%20size%20has%20become%20a%20psychological%20hurdle%20for%20investors%2C%20particularly%20among%20hedge%20funds%20and%20long-short%20investors%20who%20view%20the%20stock%20as%20a%20natural%20short%20because%20of%20its%20enormous%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoeb's%20comments%20come%20as%20investors%20debate%20whether%20the%20AI%20rally%20can%20continue%20after%20a%20historic%20run%20in%20Nvidia%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20winner%20from%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%2C%20supplying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-south-korea-ai-trade-samsung-sk-hynix-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20to%20train%20and%20run%20models%20from%20OpenAI%2C%20Google%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20other%20AI%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20surged%20nearly%2014-fold%20since%20the%20start%20of%202023%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20Wall%20Street's%20biggest%20winners%20of%20the%20AI%20era.%20The%20runup%20has%20helped%20propel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20world's%20wealthiest%20people.%20The%20stock%20is%20up%20about%2010%25%20this