e%20launched%20a%20satirical%20political%20movement%20called%20%26quot%3BCockroach%20Janta%20Party%26quot%3B%20to%20protest%20unemployment%20and%20corruption%20in%20the%20government.%3Cp%3EIshant%20Chauhan%2FHindustan%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIndian%20youth%2C%20frustrated%20with%20unemployment%20and%20corruption%2C%20are%20calling%20themselves%20cockroaches.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20created%20a%20satirical%20group%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BCockroach%20Janta%20Party%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20are%20protesting%20with%20cockroach%20masks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndia%20is%20battling%20with%20a%20high%20youth%20unemployment%20rate%2C%20with%2013.6%25%20of%20urban%20youth%20being%20jobless%20as%20of%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20heard%20of%20China's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-rat-people-broke-burnt-out-social-media-unemployment-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erat%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20now%20get%20ready%20for%20India's%20%26quot%3Bcockroaches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20hundreds%20of%20young%20Indians%20swarmed%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20Many%20wore%20masks%20depicting%20cockroach%20faces%20in%20support%20of%20a%20satirical%20movement%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BCockroach%20Janta%20Party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%26quot%3Bjanta%26quot%3B%20means%20%26quot%3Bpeople%26quot%3B%20in%20Hindi%2C%20and%20the%20CJP%20is%20a%20play%20on%20the%20name%20of%20India's%20ruling%20party%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20is%20a%20protest%20against%20high%20youth%20unemployment%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-to-india-with-family-kids-study-abroad-experience-delhi-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20subcontinent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20corruption%20in%20the%20government%2C%20and%20failures%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findia-families-paying-thousands-help-students-cheat-entrance-exams-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeducation%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%26quot%3Bcockroach%26quot%3B%20was%20inadvertently%20coined%20during%20a%20May%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20by%20India's%20chief%20justice%2C%20Surya%20Kant%2C%20who%20compared%20young%20people%20to%20unemployed%20%26quot%3Bcockroaches%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bparasites.%26quot%3B%20He%20has%20since%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20people%20with%20bogus%20degrees%2C%20not%20the%20youth%20broadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20these%20comments%2C%20an%20Indian%20based%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Abhijeet%20Dipke%2C%20posted%20on%20his%20X%20account%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20all%20cockroaches%20come%20together%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDipke%20went%20on%20to%20launch%20the%20CJP%2C%20calling%20for%20Indians%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bunemployed%2C%20lazy%2C%20chronically%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhave%20the%20ability%20to%20rant%20professionally%26quot%3B%20to%20join%20the%20movement.%20Its%20website%20reads%2C%20%26quot%3BVoice%20of%20the%20lazy%20and%20unemployed%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20political%20party%20for%20the%20people%20the%20system%20forgot%20to%20count.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20official%20Instagram%20now%20has%2022.7%20million%20followers%20as%20of%20press%20time%2C%20surpassing%20the%20ruling%20party%20BJP's%20account.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECJP's%20X%20account%2C%20which%20Dipke%20said%20was%20disabled%20for%20a%20period%2C%20has%20nearly%20300%2C000%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CJP's%20formation%20comes%20as%20India%20is%20battling%20a%20high%20youth%20unemployment%20rate.%20According%20to%20March%20statistics%20from%20the%20Indian%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%2C%20India's%20total%20unemployment%20rate%20in%202025%20for%20people%20between%2015%20and%2029%20stood%20at%209.9%25%2C%20with%20urban%20youth%20facing%20a%20higher%20rate%20of%2013.6%25.%20Millions%20of%20highly%20qualified%20young%20workers%20in%20the%20country%20are%20battling%20for%20a%20smattering%20of%20job%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECJP's%20Saturday%20protest%20in%20New%20Delhi%20was%20aimed%20directly%20at%20sacking%20India's%20education%20minister%2C%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20who%20many%20hold%20responsible%20for%20the%20recent%20scandal%20involving%20India's%20medical%20school%20entrance%20test%2C%20%26quot%3BNEET.%26quot%3B%20The%20exam%2C%20taken%20by%20millions%20of%20medical%20student%20hopefuls%2C%20was%20deemed%20invalid%20after%20the%20exam%20questions%20were%20leaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20gave%20humorous%2C%20witty%20instructions%20for%20participants%20joining%20the%20protest%20on%20Saturday%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BEat%20before%20you%20arrive.%20Revolution%20requires%20breakfast%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20movement%20is%20stronger%20when%20cockroaches%20arrive%20in%20groups.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20Gen%20Z-led%20protests%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20India%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20over%20issues%20such%20as%20unemployment%20and%20poorly%20managed%20entrance%20examinations%2C%20none%20have%20achieved%20the%20virality%20and%20social%20media%20presence%20of%20the%20CJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cockroach%20trend%20brings%20to%20mind%20other%20Gen%20Z-%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-broke-graduate-hiring-city-executive-warns-gen-z-revolt-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emillennial-led%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20have%20erupted%20across%20South%20Asia%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20Bangladesh%20and%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20China's%20%26quot%3Brat%20people%26quot%3B%20trend%20of%202025%20was%20characterized%20by%20a%20passive%2C%20quiet%20resignation%20of%20the%20country's%20youth.%20Burned%20out%20by%20Ch