Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFired%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20correspondent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-smart-people-are-saying-cbs-news-scott-pelley-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScott%20Pelley%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20CBS%20News'%20top%20editor%2C%20Bari%20Weiss%2C%20is%20directing%20coverage%20to%20be%20more%20aligned%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20appearance%20on%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20podcast%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Interview%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelley%20elaborated%20on%20his%20June%202%20statement%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%20CBS%20News'%20new%20management%20had%20instructed%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Binject%20falsehoods%20and%20bias%20into%20a%20politically%20sensitive%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20thumb%20on%20the%20scale%20for%20the%20president's%20version%20of%20events%20that%20I%20felt%20was%20a%20level%20of%20political%20influence%20that%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20in%2037%20years%20at%20CBS%20News%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelley%20told%20%26quot%3BThe%20Interview.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelley%20said%20his%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20team%20had%20produced%20a%20story%20in%20February%20detailing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafl-cio-ice-raids-minnesota-day-truth-freedom-homeland-security-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EICE%20operations%20in%20Minnesota%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20which%20agents%20shot%20and%20killed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafl-cio-ice-shooting-alex-pretti-minneapolis-border-patrol-immigration-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERenee%20Good%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20anti-ICE%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelley%20said%20Weiss%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20his%20former%20boss%2C%20Tanya%20Simon%2C%20asking%20if%20they%20could%20make%20changes%20to%20the%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20of%20the%20things%20in%20the%20email%20include%3A%20Can%20we%20make%20the%20protesters%20look%20more%20violent%3F%26quot%3B%20Pelley%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I'm%20paraphrasing.%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20quote%2C%20but%20that's%20what%20was%20communicated%20to%20me.%20And%20the%20other%20thing%20was%20Ren%C3%A9e%20Good's%20car.%20You%20need%20to%20describe%20her%20as%20driving%20toward%20the%20officer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelley%20said%20the%20second%20request%20contradicted%20video%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20over%20the%20video%20of%20the%20Ren%C3%A9e%20Good%20killing%20over%20and%20over%20and%20over%20again.%20Stop%20motion.%20Slow%20motion.%20And%20realized%20the%20event%20was%20not%20as%20the%20president%20said%20and%20not%20the%20way%20Bari%20Weiss%20remembered%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelley%20said%20Weiss%20could%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20give%20the%20Trump%20administration%20a%20fair%20shake%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20believed%20the%20requests%20were%20motivated%20by%20a%20political%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20could%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20be%20fair%20to%20the%20administration%2C%20except%20I%20felt%20that%20the%20story%20was%20abundantly%20fair%20to%20the%20administration%20and%20to%20the%20ICE%20officers%20and%20to%20the%20Border%20Patrol%20officers%20who%20were%20caught%20in%20that%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelley%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20being%20told%20to%20write%20a%20version%20of%20events%20that%20conflicted%20with%20the%20video%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20CBS%20News%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Weiss'%20request%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20political%20motivation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20email%2C%20Bari%20made%20four%20points%20in%20the%20course%20of%20editorial%20back-and-forth.%20They%20had%20no%20political%20motivation%20and%20were%20proposed%20solely%20to%20make%20the%20piece%20as%20strong%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20accurate%20as%20possible.%20As%