's%20venture%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenture%20capital%20is%20the%20financial%20engine%20of%20the%20tech%20industry.%20Founders%20with%20an%20idea%20rely%20on%20them%20to%20kick-start%20or%20turbocharge%20their%20fledgling%20companies.%20Typically%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20loan%2C%20but%20an%20equity%20exchange.%20The%20earlier%20a%20VC%20invests%2C%20the%20riskier%20the%20investment.%20When%20a%20company%20succeeds%2C%20however%2C%20the%20returns%20can%20be%20astronomical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-uber-ceo-travis-kalanick-said-he-moved-to-texas-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETravis%20Kalanick%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20responding%20to%20Isenberg%2C%20said%20that%20the%20venture%20world%20has%20changed%20over%20the%20years.%20Investors%2C%20he%20said%2C%20once%20took%20a%20more%20casual%20approach%20to%20pitch%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Kalanick%20said%20he%20pitched%20an%20investor%20who%20was%20sitting%20in%20his%20%26quot%3Bparked%20Lexus.%26quot%3B%20Kalanick%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20said%20the%20investor%20%26quot%3Bgrabbed%26quot%3B%20his%20laptop%2C%20placed%20it%20%26quot%3Bon%20his%20large%20belly%2C%26quot%3B%20pressed%20it%20against%20the%20steering%20wheel%2C%20and%20began%20flipping%20through%20the%20slides%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2001%20fundraising%20hit%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20back-and-forth%20went%20viral%20among%20the%20niche%20community%20of%20already-successful%20millionaire%20and%20billionaire%20founders%20who%20are%20terminally%20online%2C%20and%20the%20pile-on%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloudflare%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcloudflare-ceo-matthew-prince-reveals-original-idea-for-company-name-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMatthew%20Prince%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20a%20Sequoia%20partner%20passed%20on%20Cloudflare%20because%20%26quot%3Bhe%20didn't%20think%20a%20woman%20could%20lead%20a%20security%20infrastructure%20company.%26quot%3B%20Cloudflare%20was%20founded%20in%202009%20by%20Prince%2C%20Lee%20Holloway%2C%20and%20Michelle%20Zatlyn.%20The%20internet%20services%20company%20is%20now%20valued%20at%20almost%20%2490%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrince%20said%20he%20also%20once%20met%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-5-year-olds-wont-need-job-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKhosla%20Ventures%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20investing%20in%20Cloudflare's%20Series%20C.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVinod%20Khosla%2C%20the%20legendary%20tech%20investor%20and%20the%20firm's%20namesake%2C%20took%20Prince%20and%20his%20fellow%20founders%20out%20to%20dinner%2C%20Prince%20wrote.%20Near%20the%20end%20of%20the%20conversation%2C%20Prince%20recalled%2C%20Khosla%20leaned%20over%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20impressed%20with%20you%2C%20not%20so%20much%20with%20them%2C%20what%20if%20you%20fire%20them%20and%20I'll%20give%20you%20all%20their%20stock%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrince%20said%20he%20was%20so%20offended%20he%20never%20spoke%20to%20Khosla%20again.%20Other%20founders%20responded%20to%20Prince%2C%20adding%20their%20own%20experiences%20dealing%20with%20Khosla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20enough%20for%20Khosla%20to%20spend%20his%20Saturday%20responding%20to%20the%20accusations%2C%20firing%20off%20over%20a%20dozen%20X%20posts.%20In%20some%2C%20he%20denied%20the%20stories%20and%20asked%20for%20evidence%2C%20but%20in%20most%2C%20he%20repeated%20a%20single%20mantra%3A%20Honesty%20is%20the%20best%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20often%20wrong%20but%20always%20give%20honest%20opinions.%20Some%20find%20this%20harsh%2C%20but%20hypocritical%20politeness%20hurts%20founders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20one%20post.%20%26quot%3BBrutal%20honesty%20gives%20them%20a%20chance%20to%20evaluate%20it%20and%20accept%20or%20reject%20the%20opinion.%20Great%20founders%20elect%20for%20honesty.%20It%20is%20not%20fun%20to%20offer%20brutal%20honesty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosla%20Ventures%20declined%20to%20comment%20when%20reached%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20industry%20insiders%20came%20to%20Khosla's%20defense.%20Blake%20Byers%2C%20an%20early-stage%20investor%20and%20founder%2C%20said%20Khosla%20founded%20one%20of%20the%20pioneering%20companies%20of%20the%20modern%20computer%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20Sun%20Microsystems%20%E2%80%94%20before%20becoming%20one%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20most%20influential%20venture%20capitalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20one%20of%20the%20truest%20VCs%20to%20ever%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.x.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EApologies%2C%20I%20may%20sometimes%20be%20wrong%2C%20but%20I%20will%20always%20give%20entrepreneurs%20my%20best%20and%20honest%20opinion%2C%20popular%20or%20not.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmxtSeepnIT%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmxtSeepnIT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Vinod%20Khosla%20(%40vkhosla)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fvkhosla%2Fstatus%2F2063422271117824425%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%207%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Cummins%2C%20an%20angel%20investor%20and%20robotics%20expert%2C%20said%20he%20began%20pitching%20a%20partner%20at%20a%20French%20firm%2C%20only%20for%20the%20investor%20to%20interrupt%20with%20questions%20about%20his%20parents'%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20your%20father%20do%3F'%20the%20partner%20asks%20me%20in%20a%20thick%20French%20accent%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Cummins%20said%20his%20fath